SELECT Substring(ca_zip, 1, 5) AS ca_zip, 
               Count(*) AS cnt 
FROM   customer_address 
WHERE  ca_address_sk IN (SELECT c_current_addr_sk 
                          FROM   customer 
                          WHERE  c_preferred_cust_flag = 'Y')
GROUP BY Substring(ca_zip, 1, 5)
